snippet.title: Beyonce’s Mom FINALLY SPEAKS On Beyonce’s Worsening Mental Health
snippet.description:
Beyonce’s Mom FINALLY SPEAKS On Beyonce’s Worsening Mental Health

Is Jay-Z always rubbing Beyonce’s leg in public because Bey is suffering from a mental health disorder?
There’s been a lot of speculation lately about the famous “Jayonce leg rub” among Beyonce’s fans, and now we’re finally hearing from Ms.Tina Knowles herself about the real reason Jay always touches Beyonce’s leg in social situations and if bey really suffers from any mental health issues.
So what did Bey’s mom reveal?
